 />\n<br />\n久而久之，一天中，最能令我思想最清晰的，就是抽煙的時刻了。」 ----- &lt;&lt;一生中的最愛&gt;&gt; 作者： Diego_Costa @ HKG<br />\n<br />\n根本男人食煙就係型。係男人既浪漫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔食煙根本無資格做男人！！！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咁講係通既<br />\n咁將成篇既主角轉做毒品都得嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bde859b7b7222c4ce7df2155d492b6382efa8a","tid":466180,"uid":137884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"咁你食多啲啦<br />\n好快地球就會少個死煙剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c4217ddbb77870d33cfd0e7da7070f6ec8408e","tid":466180,"uid":29087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"食到牙都黃埋 嘩 真係好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f540b4a9ee2d8101ea4729c582eb2bd75c7c98","tid":466180,"uid":71878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>型唔型睇個樣<br />\n關食煙撚事咩</blockquote><br />\n好似樓主咁點食都唔會型"},{"pid":"1352310008b8c0555fb4fa29357769b94c31cf58","tid":466180,"uid":435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"要靠食煙先型嘅人型極有限啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f357ce0d8a8cb218cbe5675684bcc7cce5cab303","tid":466180,"uid":14965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"食煙既男人有佬味同成熟D，我會加佢分"},{"pid":"176dc73c0b3603c6ead76312767190c8302ba33a","tid":466180,"uid":49634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"屌 啲阿叔食到牙又黃 又成陣煙臭味 真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298446da90d519809870e85289bcae028281ba8f","tid":466180,"uid":12980,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"我仲會周街噴<br />\n幫個啲冇錢買煙既人都有得享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma